name: Rendezvous
comments: Finally released with modern vocal overdubs, this was one of the first songs recorded during the 'Darkness on the Edge of Town' sessions. At the time, it was kept off the album because it didn’t fit thematically. First played live August 1, 1976 at Monmouth County Arts Center, Red Bank (NJ). In 1998, Bruce already released a December 1980 live version on Tracks .
